{"tid":1574922,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"郭富城 光復香港Medley | 國貨城光復精選大碟｜反送中","createTime":"2019-09-16T15:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T17:09:28.000Z","uid":38737,"like":99,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"7b1bc68d9a1fa69cc07c26f5c2e39106215a215c","tid":1574922,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:39:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ifYvLqeGy-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FifYvLqeGy-M&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=dbc6fad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ifYvLqeGy-M</a><br />\n<br />\n#郭富城 #銅鑼灣 #國貨城<br />\n國貨城2019光復精選大碟已經推出，收錄精選歌曲包括：<br />\n《勇者歌》,《狂武之城》,《鐵路困惑》,《PoPo失憶諒解備忘錄》,《棍的呼喚》，實有一首岩你聽！<br />\n<br />\n《勇者歌》 原曲：唱這歌<br />\n 改詞：梁栢堅and fans <br />\n《鐵路困惑》 原曲：鐵幕誘惑 <br />\n改詞：大B *打你老母<br />\n《狂武之城》原曲：狂野之城 <br />\n改詞：伍君 *大B<br />\n《棍的呼喚》原曲：愛的呼喚<br />\n改詞：Ki Mak<br />\n《PoPo失憶諒解備忘錄》原曲：失憶諒解備忘錄 <br />\n改詞：妁小汀 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9933b349253f3ea83c3d708887c9e89e01bfdb07","tid":1574922,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:40:00.000Z","msg":"915國旗行動好成功!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573307</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jR5wr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jR5wr1.jpg&h=d9b2c693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1d5c6edb59ea7df694ce50d46c1af5b63329f8a","tid":1574922,"uid":173058,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"呂麗搖巴肯覆我未？咩plan都冇就洗bot叫人入去機場送頭好不負責任。<br />\n你一日唔講922點入機場、有咩plan我都會問落去。<br />\n3條link咩內容都冇，吹1點嘅雞但叫人1230睇連登/Tg等消息係咩玩法<br />\n比你地班機場Admin撚足3次，唔想再有人被撚<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash